title: Previewing Week 1 Road Tests
description:
Wendi Nix, Sam Acho, and Steve Coughlin take a look at some games that could lead to some early upsets. Plus, Pete Thamel joins the show from Columbus, OH to discuss the Buckeyes, and Tiffany Greene and Jay Walker share news and notes for some notable HBCU matchups this weekend.
